<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Deleted</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 32px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    .email-header {
      background-color: #6b7280;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 32px 24px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Account Permanently Deleted</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p class="greeting">Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Your IT Job Portal account has been permanently deleted as requested. All your personal data has been removed from our systems.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <strong>What was deleted:</strong>
        <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
          <li>Account credentials and personal information</li>
          <li>CV profile and career data</li>
          <li>Chat conversation history</li>
          <li>Job subscriptions</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0;">Your job applications have been anonymised to preserve records for companies that reviewed them.</p>
      </div>

      <p>If you ever want to use IT Job Portal again in the future, you are welcome to create a new account.</p>
      <p>We are sorry to see you go and wish you all the best in your career journey.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      &copy; {{currentYear}} IT Job Portal. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
